#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_hashingcontext.rst:19
msgid ""
"The HashingContext class provides an interface for computing "
"cryptographic hashes over multiple iterations. This is useful for example"
" when computing hashes of big files (so you don't have to load them all "
"in memory), network streams, and data streams in general (so you don't "
"have to hold buffers)."
msgstr ""

